Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io

This package contains the BPEL reader and writer interfaces and the factory classes to access them.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeBpelClassConstants Defines all of the class constants used by IAeBpelDefWriters, IAeBpelDefReaders, and the corresponding registries.
IAeBpelFactory Factory for reading and writing BPEL.
IAeBpelLegacyConstants Interface for attribute or element names that changed from version 1.1 to 2.0.
IAeBpelReader Interface for working with BPEL deserializers.
IAeBpelWriter Interface for working with BPEL serializers.
IAeCorrelationPatternIO Provides the legal values for the correlation initiation/validation patterns
 

Class Summary
AeAbstractBpelFactory A base class for the BPEL factories.
AeBpelIO Wraps the basic serialization/deserialization calls currently in use.
AeBPWSFactory Default factory for BPEL4WS 1.1.
AeBPWSUtil A Util class that has some convenience methods for working with the def layer for BPEl4WS 1.1.
AeCommentIO Handles the details of reading and writing comments during BPEL process serialization/deserialization.
AeCorrelationPatternIOFactory factory for creating a class for reading/writing the correlation pattern value for a correlation.
AeCorrelationPatternIOFactory.AeBaseCorrelationPatternIO I/O class that reads/writes correlation pattern types to/from strings given the legal values for the pattern attribute.
AeWSBPELAbstractProcessFactory Factory for WSBPEL 2.0 Abstract processes.
AeWSBPELFactory BPEL factory for WSBPEL4 2.0.
 

Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io Description

This package contains the BPEL reader and writer interfaces and the factory classes to access them.
